## Determinism Checklist (For Your Review Role)

When another agent's PR touches sim logic, verify:

- [ ] No `time.time()` or `pygame.time.get_ticks()` in sim paths
- [ ] No `random.*` globals — must use `game.sim.determinism.get_rng("subsystem")`
- [ ] No `set()` iteration where order affects game state
- [ ] No `hash()` as stable keys
- [ ] New fields on Hero/Building/Enemy don't store wall-clock time
- [ ] New events include `x, y` positions so audio visibility gating works
- [ ] Audio triggers are event-driven, not sim-tick-driven

